headline: Bank of America Reaffirms Buy on Amcor (AMCR), Raises Target to $56
summary: Amcor plc (NYSE:AMCR) is included among the 13 Cheapest Dividend Aristocrats to Invest in. On February 4, Bank of America lifted its price recommendation on Amcor plc (NYSE:AMCR) to $56 from $48.40. The firm also reiterated its Buy rating on the stock. After going through the fiscal Q2 numbers, analysts slightly trimmed their EPS estimates, […]
